        KEYWORDS="utils"
           SHORT="Monitoring program for motherboards"
cat << EOF
xmbmon is a monitoring program for motherboards which can monitor the CPU
temperatures and the frequency of CPU cooling fans, etc. The package includes
"mbmon", which can be used at the commandline to report the temperatures,
voltages, and RPM (rounds per minute) of the fans, and "xmbmon", which displays
the three temperatures and a core voltage as simple curves.
EOF
